                               }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id" : "introduction",
                    "text" : [ { "text" : "### Introduction\n\nLetters of the alphabet group together to form syllables. A better understanding of this process helps us differentiate and comprehend words more clearly.\n\nIn this text, we will explore the structure of words in greater depth. At the end, we will present a game to reinforce this knowledge",
                                 "source" : null,
                                 "isTable" : false,
                                 "date_time" : null,
                                 "format" : "markdown",
                                 "PostMention": "."
                               }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id" : "game",
                    "text" : [ 
                               { "text" : "<h3>Game</h3><b>Goal:</b> Your challenge is to identify vowels (V) and consonants (C) that form a syllable. For each correct answer, you will be introduced to a different Indigenous region of the Americas (<i>Abya Ayala</i>).</p><p><b>Rules: </b>Use the arrow keys (<i class=\"fa-solid fa-caret-up\" style=\"font-size:1.5em;color:#0f0\"></i> and <i class=\"fa-solid fa-caret-down\" style=\"font-size:1.5em;color:#00f;\" id=\"traineeDown0\"></i>) to switch between consonants (C) and vowels (V). To move to the next syllable, click on <i class=\"fa-solid fa-play\" style=\"color: Tomato;\"></i>",
                                 "source" : null,
                                  "date_time" : null,
                                  "isTable" : false,
                                  "format" : "html",
                                  "PostMention": " "
                               },
                               { "text" : "<table id=\"yupana1\" class=\"tawapukllay\"><tr><th colspan=\"3\">Classify each letter as a consonant (C) or a vowel (V).</th><th>Controls</th></tr> <tr id=\"tf1\"><td id=\"tc1f1\" colspan=\"3\">&nbsp;</td> <td id=\"tc4f1\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-caret-up\" style=\"font-size:5em;color:#0f0\"></i></td></tr> <tr id=\"tf2\"><td id=\"tc1f2\" colspan=\"3\"><span id=\"cv0\"></span>&nbsp;<span id=\"cv1\"></span></div></td> <td id=\"tc4f2\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-caret-down\" style=\"font-size:5em;color:#00f;\" id=\"traineeDown0\"></i></td></tr> <tr id=\"tf3\"><td colspan=\"3\" id=\"tc1f3\"><span id=\"gameImage\"></span></td><td id=\"tc4f3\"><div id=\"descImage\"></div> <span style=\"font-size: 3em; color: Tomato;\"><i id=\"nextLevel\" class=\"fa-solid fa-play\"></i></span></td></tr> </table>",
                                 "source" : null,
                                  "date_time" : null,
                                  "isTable" : false,
                                  "format" : "html",
                                  "PostMention": " "
                               }
                    ]
                },
